
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>

    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VAC-GO</title>

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="./css/materialize.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="./css/app.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="navbar-fixed">
      <nav>
        <div class="nav-wrapper blue">
          <span class="brand-logo center">VAC-Go!</span>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div> <!-- end of navbar-fixed -->
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col s12">
        <ul class="tabs">
          <li class="tab col l4 m4 s4"><a class="active" href="#login">Login</a></li>
          <li class="tab col l4 m4 s4"><a href="#signup">Sign Up</a></li>
          <li class="tab col l4 m4 s4"><a href="#help">Help</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div id="login" class="container">
        <form class="col l12 m12 s12">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="input-field col l12 m12 s12">
              <i class="material-icons prefix">account_circle</i>
              <input id="username" type="text">
              <label for="username">Username</label>
            </div>
            <div class="input-field col l12 m12 s12">
              <i class="material-icons prefix">lock_outline</i>
              <input id="password" type="password">
              <label for="password">Password</label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row center">
            <button class="btn waves-effect waves-light" type="button">
              Log In<i class="material-icons right">send</i>
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div id="signup" class="container">
        <form class="col l12 m12 s12">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="input-field col l12 m12 s12">
              <i class="material-icons prefix">email</i>
              <input id="email" type="email" class="validate" />
              <label for="email" data-error="Bad email format!" data-success="Looks good!">Email</label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="input-field col l12 m12 s12">
              <i class="material-icons prefix">account_circle</i>
              <input id="username" type="text" class="validate" />
              <label for="username" data-success="Looks good!">Username</label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="input-field col l6 m12 s12">
              <i class="material-icons prefix">lock_open</i>
              <input id="password" type="password" class="validate" pattern=".{5,10}" />
              <label for="password" data-error="Password not of correct length!" data-success="Looks good!">Password</label>
            </div>
            <div class="input-field col l6 m12 s12">
              <i class="material-icons prefix">lock_outline</i>
              <input id="confPassword" type="password" class="validate" />
              <label for="confPassword" data-error="Passwords don't match!" data-success="Looks good!">Confirm Password</label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row center">
            <a href="/signed-in" class="btn waves-effect waves-light">
              Sign Up<i class="material-icons right">send</i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div id="help" class="container">
        <div class="col l12 m12 s12">
          <h4>About</h4>
          <p class="flow-text">
            VAC-Go is a forum designed to help UCSD students collaborate and receive guidance on their course plans
            from both their counselors and other students.
          </p>
          <p class="flow-text">
            Users are encouraged to post their potential course plans to the site to allow other users (who have taken
            the same or similar work load) to comment on and provide feedback about professors/TAs, and just helpful
            tips in general for their peers. On the other side, each user is encouraged to spread their knowledge of
            the courses they have taken by commenting on and/or voting on other users' posts.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col l12 m12 s12">
          <h4>Contact</h4>
          <p class="flow-text">
            Feel free to email us at support@vacGo.com with any questions, comments, concerns, bugs, or suggestions!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="./js/jquery-3.1.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="./js/materialize.min.js"></script>
    <script src="./js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="./js/login.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
